1.3.1
=====

2020-03-31

* Version and functionality did not change.
* Move NLS tools to usr/share/doc/nls/<project-name>/.

1.3.1
=====

2019-11-04

* Fix error "invalid window id".
* Test with yad-lib 1.2.0.

1.3.0
=====

2019-10-17

* Re-released for scripts-to-go.
* No new functionality; equivalent to version 1.2.1 for Fatdog64-721...802.
* New packaging with installer/uninstaller.
* Add README and manual page.
* Change TEXTDOMAIN.
* Add .desktop file and icons.

1.2.1
=====

2018-11-30

* Release for Fatdog64-721 and follow-on versions.
* No new functionality.
* Update icon and translation template.

1.2.0
=====

2018-08-01
* No new functionality.
* New requirement: yad-lib 1.0.0 or higher.

1.1.0
=====

2017-12-10

* First release for Fatdog64-720
* Require: shnetlib 1.2.0 or higher.
* Keep position of dragged-around main dialog and popups.
* Update .pot file for translations.
* Update xgettext.sh tool for translators.
* Replace column "Reason" with more-capable column "Details".
* Auto-detect interface status and IP address changes, show in "Details".
* Add help popup and tooltip for hard-blocked interface.
* Fix 'Restart Network' button (it wasn't acted upon).
* Work-around for BusyBox v1.27.0.git-2017-11-11.
* Performance improvements.

1.0.3
=====

2017-09-18

* Add message "Wireless interface not found".

