=====

2017-08-21

* Add icons.
* See README

1.0.1
=====

2017-08-20

* Updates for shnetlib 1.1.0
* Fix: Handle kernel modules that don't support rfkill.
* i18n: Add some new messages.
* Require: shnetlib 1.1.0 or higher.

1.0.0
=====

2017-08-11

* First public version.
* Includes section on porting to other Linux.

